        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4271289946" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15532017708415406514">The Lighthouse Effect: How Ordinary People Can Have an Extraordinary Impact in the World by Steve Pemberton is the follow-up book to his highly successful first book, A Chance in the World. Steve had a horrible childhood, ending up in foster. Those experiences fostered his need to write these inspiring books and bring hope to many people. It&apos;s amazing how certain people in our lives show up at the right time, providing solace and a positive force. In the author&apos;s experience, these people kept hi</span>
  <span id="freeText15532017708415406514" style="display:none">The Lighthouse Effect: How Ordinary People Can Have an Extraordinary Impact in the World by Steve Pemberton is the follow-up book to his highly successful first book, A Chance in the World. Steve had a horrible childhood, ending up in foster. Those experiences fostered his need to write these inspiring books and bring hope to many people. It's amazing how certain people in our lives show up at the right time, providing solace and a positive force. In the author's experience, these people kept him going, even in very small ways, by giving books to him, and being mentors as well. This is an emotional and inspirational read and one worth delving into. You will find that you can relate easily to the author and what he went through. You may even be a lighthouse in someone's life, without even realizing it. Highly recommend.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15532017708415406514" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


