<span id="freeTextContainer5828981377386970903">In the lighthouse affect Mr. Pemberton tells us about the Award winning foster family he was placed with after his father died. Unfortunately they didn’t deserve awards and verbally abused him. By the end of the first chapter you’re going to need tissues. And by the end of the book you’re going to admire him. Although this is his second memoir it isn’t light on inspiration and great stories. They have lots of takeaways and great sayings and I found this book easy to read and very enjoyable. I lo</span>
  <span id="freeText5828981377386970903" style="display:none">In the lighthouse affect Mr. Pemberton tells us about the Award winning foster family he was placed with after his father died. Unfortunately they didn’t deserve awards and verbally abused him. By the end of the first chapter you’re going to need tissues. And by the end of the book you’re going to admire him. Although this is his second memoir it isn’t light on inspiration and great stories. They have lots of takeaways and great sayings and I found this book easy to read and very enjoyable. I love reading about things that inspire people and their personal stories of struggles and overcoming those struggles and if you like books like that you’ll like this book. I totally did! I highly recommend this book especially for those who just need a little lift me up, because they have passages that you could read on the go that can either be a clarifying moment or an aha moment. This was a really good book.</span>
